	SURVEYPAGES
*******************************************************************************************************************
*******************************************************************************************************************

<surveypage IRI1>
/caption ="The following statements inquire about your thoughts and feelings in a variety of situations.
 
For each item, indicate how well it describes you by choosing the appropriate letter on the scale under each question: A, B, C, D, or E. 

READ EACH ITEM CAREFULLY BEFORE RESPONDING. Answer as honestly as you can. Thank you.
"
/questions = [1 = q1_FS, q2_EC]
</surveypage>

<surveypage IRI2>
/caption ="READ EACH ITEM CAREFULLY BEFORE RESPONDING. Answer as honestly as you can. Thank you.
"
